Please report bugs at https://developer.berlios.de/bugs/?group_id=5564

Remember to insert in the report any information useful to reproduce
and fix the problem, insert AT LEAST the following:
	* Operating system (distribution, version)
	* Tor version (specify if you installed a packaged version or
	  if you compiled Tor from source).
	* GTK and GNOME versions.
	* Python, pygtk, gnome-python versions.

If you start the program from the command lind typing
	torapplet0.py run-in-window
	
the error messages will be displayed on the terminal. If you can
reproduce the bug running the program this way, please insert in your
report any error message you receive.
